    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for anyone seeking low-cost transportation or a worthwhile project. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it still presents a strong value opportunity at this price point. A smart buy for budget-minded drivers, first-time owners, or anyone looking for dependable potential without a big upfront investment.",
