      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a solid opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a first car, or an affordable project. It\u2019s priced with its age and wear in mind, and I\u2019m aiming to be straightforward so there are no surprises. If you want an honest, inexpensive car that could still serve well with a little TLC, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for an enthusiast or budget-minded driver looking for a usable project with real potential. This car shows its age cosmetically and is being sold in poor condition, but it still offers a responsive powertrain, composed road manners, and the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes ownership approachable. A great candidate for someone who appreciates analog feel and doesn\u2019t mind putting in a little TLC to bring it back. Priced to move and well worth a look if you want affordable entry into a genuinely engaging car.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Used and rough, priced to move. Great budget buy for work, errands, or a backup ride.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of old-school character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still turns errands into a little adventure. It\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly ride with plenty of personality, ideal for someone who appreciates a vehicle with presence and sees the appeal in bringing out its next chapter. Whether you want an affordable runabout, a hands-on project, or a distinctive car with real story and soul, this one offers a rare chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
